duties_responsibilities.duty: Perform physical warehouse tasks such as loading, unloading, and sorting packages of various sizes.
Adhere to a fast-paced work environment and maintain physical fitness to handle the demands of the job.
Work one shift a day for part-time employees and two shifts for full-time employees. Shift lengths vary based on package volume.
Balance work and personal life through flexible scheduling.
Receive generous paid time off and valuable employee discounts on various products and services.

education_certification.credential: High School Diploma or GED equivalent
